{"tid":954632,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去咗冬日美食節？","createTime":"2018-12-24T17:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T09:28:27.000Z","uid":10330,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bc0bf3122df34001f2d987cc38b689c7be6488","tid":954632,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:42:08.000Z","msg":"好撚伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一入場個hall完全煙霧離漫 <br />\n係室內賣串燒 大煙到仆街<br />\n成件衫吸曬油煙味 行到最尾果行<br />\n地下仲要痴笠笠<br />\n有6-7成賣海味<br />\n好多野食賣 我試咗幾樣都係伏<br />\n質素好差 <br />\n第一次去亦都係最後一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去返工展會好過 <br />\n早放諗唔到同女朋友去邊hea<br />\n咁岩老母俾咗2張飛 唔係都唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d21546145c08325f47cd829bbeacce80442e25","tid":954632,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"仲諗住聽日去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd6c9fe7a69075387ca7c77d0e81e2bd98eb6d5","tid":954632,"uid":68390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:54:34.000Z","msg":"暑假嗰個美饂節氣氛相對好少少<br />\n冬日美食節好多講唔出嘅牌子<br />\n又勁多大陸/台灣嘅攤擋<br />\n有擋仲要試食懶人火鍋，睇到眼都突埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805c9ce51a2d5cb5ad9d11c67bda50160e2f0b94","tid":954632,"uid":68390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暑假嗰個美<span style=\"color: red;\">食</span>節氣氛相對好少少<br />\n冬日美食節好多講唔出嘅牌子<br />\n又勁多大陸/台灣嘅攤擋<br />\n有擋仲要試食懶人火鍋，睇到眼都突埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9122f4969ab7134f51e5ceebe2e91c3838a253f3","tid":954632,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd6c9fe7a69075387ca7c77d0e81e2bd98eb6d5","tid":954632,"uid":68390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy"