,"quote":{"pid":"fc5f68e802fcfd799da735c3a95f02cff4e1d948","tid":954632,"uid":185092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:07:10.000Z","msg":"上年去過 迫過二穴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:11:48.000Z","msg":"今日唔逼 都有大陸人去"},{"pid":"602da9f973028a3d85d02457558331343531594d","tid":954632,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:16:36.000Z","msg":"夏天個美食節都係一樣垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452e5d42e6a732136952982c0579533dc2626346","tid":954632,"uid":47452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:17:42.000Z","msg":"我星期日同呀媽去<br />\n最尾一行真係行到人都癲<br />\n又逼，啲油煙成個場都係<br />\n陣味勁到以為自己去完BBQ嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab250eea3018bb49f5d4f100aa4defaa2127f39d","tid":954632,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"又話好多野食<br />\n都冇樣好食 又極少試食<br />\n啲嘢食好多重覆 串燒 玉子燒 燒蠔 燒帶子嗰堆<br />\n魚蛋 公仔麵 腸仔都賣一餐<br />\n有啲仲要喺你面前煎急凍食品 <br />\n三十幾四十蚊叫你買一份 算點"},{"pid":"e3725cc1351bb9b479d5be19d002adf2fdf4e0d2","tid":954632,"uid":71671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T01:48:10.000Z","msg":"我仲派左成三十張飛出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲諗緊如果呢兩日冇野做就同女朋友去tim...而家可以慳返。"},{"pid":"83a56fc737e548f33b777c7abe544305270cdf11","tid":954632,"uid":73972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"我去得幾開心，十蚊粒煎帶子，仲要幾大粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1c52df0dba6706fa89a330d4b1eda49e95061c","tid":954632,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"工展會好過啦"},{"pid":"f54c8c172d12b25968440224cd3fbbf9b731e31e","tid":954632,"uid":194281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"睇到價錢都無興趣,蚵仔煎要30蚊....仲未講要20蚊入場<img src=\"/assets/face